## Five Non-Negotiable Risk Rules
1. Max 2 orders per cycle -- Knight Capital prevention
2. Order fill verification before stop loss placed
3. Daily 3% loss limit circuit breaker
4. Friday short close rule -- all shorts closed by 3:30 PM ET, no new shorts after 2 PM ET
5. Stop loss placed atomically with every entry -- if stop fails position closes immediately

